    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<pre><code class="bash postgresql setup">sudo pacman -S postgresql
sudo -i -u postgres
initdb --locale en_US.UTF-8 -E UTF8 -D '/var/lib/postgres/data'
exit
sudo systemctl start postgresql
sudo systemctl enable postgresql
sudo -i -u postgres
createuser ck -P -S -R -D
createdb -O ck msf
</code></pre>

<p><blockquote><p>I shall be a denizen of the undeground or a successfull man of the world.<br/>There shall be no compromise!</p><footer><strong>ck</strong></footer></blockquote></p>
